headline: Costco is pushing back — hard — against the anti-DEI movement
summary: Walmart, John Deere, Tractor Supply and other companies are changing or walking away from diversity, equity and inclusion (DEI) programs in response to right-wing pressure. But Costco believes DEI improves its business and is standing behind its efforts.

headline: My 3 Favorite Stocks to Buy Right Now
summary: Costco Wholesale (NASDAQ: COST) has steadily grown revenue and profit over time, even through difficult market environments.  One thing I like a lot about Costco is that its main profit driver is one you can count on, and it's high margin.  With renewal rates above 92% in the U.S. and Canada, it's clear shoppers are sticking with Costco year after year.
